	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et pacem a domino per Iesum Christum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Siehe oben <ref target="file11066">Nr. 1024</ref>.</note> superioribus diebus, dum essem Isnę una cum charissimo nostro fratre <persName ref="person28">Butzero</persName>, atque literas per d[ominum] doctorem Zwickium ad te deferri curabam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ubi vero <placeName ref="place565">Constantiam</placeName> meae, quas tibi destinaram, pervenissent litere, aberat Io[annes] Zwickius, quo factum est, ut invita prochrastinatione ad te non pervenerint.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim diaconus nostrae <placeName ref="place697">Memmingensis</placeName> ecclesiae<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="person2015">Hans Salb</persName>, 1532-1538 Helfer bei St. Martin in <placeName ref="place697">Memmingen</placeName> (s. Hermann Erhard, Memminger Pfarrerbuch, Neustadt a. d. Aisch 1977, S. 17).</note>, in domino cooperarius meus, <placeName ref="place565">Constantiam</placeName> abiturus pollicebatur et nomine meo velle tuam humanitatem invisere, cui quoque literas dedi tibi deferendas.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed corporis aegritudine interceptus cogebatur relicto itinere Tigurum versus Memingam remeare, ubi iam altera vice spe mea frustratus sum.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed quia michi persuasi<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>vor</hi> persuasi <hi>gestrichenes</hi> per[...].</note> meas literas, quas ab Isna scripsi, ad tuas pervenisse manus, hortor per dominum, amice incomparabilis, ut saltem uno verbo respondeas, ut, si quid animi sunt raritatis mucore obsiti atque non nichil superati, denuo a situ vindicati foelicius coeant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego de adventu meo (quem iam altera vice tentavi) nondum plane despondi animum, immo constitui te tuamque familiam invisere.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cogor tamen ob praesentem necessitatem moras nectere.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Uxor enim mea<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">[...], geb. Lübegger (vgl. HBBW I <ref target="file10071">[Nr. 43]</ref>, S. 222, Anm. 4).</note> graviter gestans uterum fere parturire incipit.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">At<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>vor</hi> At <hi>verschmiertes, unlesbares Wort.</hi></note> postquam fęliciter pepererit, accingam me itineri<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Vgl. auch unten <ref target="file11085">Nr. 1043</ref>, 36f, und 1058, 9f.</note>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ora dominum, mi frater, hos ut conatus meos suo spiritu provehat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale in domino, charissime frater, et me pristino amore prosequere.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta nomine nostro dilectam tibi coniugem<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Anna, geb. Adlischwyler.</note> atque matrem<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Anna, geb. Wiederkehr.</note>, <persName ref="person114">Leonem Iude</persName> et <persName ref="person165">Pellicanum</persName>.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spiritus domini sit semper tecum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="235"/>Datum 9. septembris, Memminge, anno 1537.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="person195">Gervasius</persName> Scolasticus<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>Über der Zeile von Simlers Hand:</hi> Gervasius Scolasticus.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magnae pietatis et eruditionis viro ac domino Heinricho Bullingero, Tigurinę ecclesie antistiti vigilantissimo, praeceptori ac fratri cum primis observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
